article_id:1730,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue with the Fallen Wings Wyrmprint [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603873800"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>Players who did not fully unbind or fully unlock copies of this wyrmrprint while these issues were in effect will be sent goodwill gestures in the form of eldwater, as described below.<br><br>■Affected Players and Eldwater Goodwill Gesture Amounts<br>Goodwill gestures will be given separately for unbinds and copies.<br><br>[Unbinds]<br>・Players who did not possess the Fallen Wings wyrmprint before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 14,250 eldwater<br>・Players who did not unbind the Fallen Wings wyrmprint even once after the Version 2.0.0 update and before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span> (regardless of how far it was already unbound): 14,250 eldwater<br>・Players whose Fallen Wings wyrmprint was unbound at least once at the time of the release of the Version 2.0.0 update, then unbound three times before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 2,850 eldwater<br>・Players whose Fallen Wings wyrmprint was unbound at least once at the time of the release of the Version 2.0.0 update, then unbound two times before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 6,650 eldwater<br>・Players whose Fallen Wings wyrmprint was unbound at least once at the time of the release of the Version 2.0.0 update, then unbound one time before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 10,450 eldwater<br>・Players whose Fallen Wings wyrmprint was unbound from stage 0 to stage 3 between the release of the Version 2.0.0 update and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 3,800 eldwater<br>・Players whose Fallen Wings wyrmprint was unbound from stage 0 to stage 2 between the release of the Version 2.0.0 update and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 7,600 eldwater<br>・Players whose Fallen Wings wyrmprint was unbound from stage 0 to stage 1 between the release of the Version 2.0.0 update and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 11,400 eldwater<br><br>[Copies]<br>・Players who did not add copies before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 48,450 eldwater<br>・Players who added 1 copy before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 32,300 eldwater<br>・Players who added 2 copies before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>: 16,150 eldwater<br><br>■Goodwill Gesture Timing<br>Goodwill gestures will be provided starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603933200"></span>. This can be claimed from your goodie box upon arrival.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>The following issues have affected the Fallen Wings wyrmprint since the Version 2.0.0 update:</div><div><br></div><div>・Its HP and strength values are lower than intended.</div><div>・The costs to unbind and unlock copies are lower than intended.</div><div><br></div><div>[Incorrect]</div><div>■Unbinds</div><div>Eldwater needed for 0 &rarr; 1: 150</div><div>Eldwater needed for 1 &rarr; 2: 200</div><div>Eldwater needed for 2 &rarr; 3: 200</div><div>Eldwater needed for 3 &rarr; 4: 200</div><div><br></div><div>■Copies</div><div>Eldwater needed for 1 &rarr; 2: 850</div><div>Eldwater needed for 2 &rarr; 3: 850</div><div>Eldwater needed for 3 &rarr; 4: 850</div><div><br></div><div>[Correct]</div><div>■Unbinds</div><div>Eldwater needed for 0 &rarr; 1: 3,000</div><div>Eldwater needed for 1 &rarr; 2: 4,000</div><div>Eldwater needed for 2 &rarr; 3: 4,000</div><div>Eldwater needed for 3 &rarr; 4: 4,000</div><div><br></div><div>■Copies</div><div>Eldwater needed for 1 &rarr; 2: 17,000</div><div>Eldwater needed for 2 &rarr; 3: 17,000</div><div>Eldwater needed for 3 &rarr; 4: 17,000</div><div><br></div><div>These issues were addressed in a data update around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1603778400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1603778400,update_time1603873960